after them

*Razgovor* je bio zanimljiv. (The conversation was interesting.)
Njih dvoje su se dugo *razgovarali*. (The two of them talked for a long time.)
Nismo čuli šta se *razgovara*. (We didn't hear what they were talking about.)
Nisu mogli da se dogovore tokom *razgovora*. (They couldn't agree during the conversation.)
Ona je bila ugodna tokom *razgovora*. (She was pleasant during the conversation.)